  "markup": "\u003Cdiv id=\u0022content_0_controls_0_pnlImage\u0022 class=\u0022content-image content-image-right\u0022\u003E\r\n\t\t\r\n        \r\n    \r\n\t\u003C/div\u003E\r\n\t\t    \u003Cp\u003ELaser Therapy U. LLC reserves a right to cancel and/or reject customers account at its own discretion. In case of closure of an account, Laser Therapy U. LLC will issue a full or partial credit based on prorated term of membership.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EDELIVERY SCHEDULE\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EPURCHASED RESEARCH DOCUMENTS AND WEBINARS\u003C/h3\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EOnce your account has been authorized by Laser Therapy U, any purchased research documents and webinars will be processed upon purchase, and will be able to be downloaded/viewed immediately.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EPURCHASED ITEMS FROM LASER THERAPY U BOOKSTORE\u003C/h3\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EWe will attempt to process your order the next business day after your order is placed. We will normally ship your order within 2 business days after order entry via UPS Ground shipping service. International orders ship via UPS or USPS Services.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EREFUND/RETURN POLICY\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EPURCHASED RESEARCH DOCUMENTS AND WEBINARS\u003C/h3\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you purchased an individual research document or Webinar and are not completely satisfied, please notify us within 24 hours of your purchase.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EPURCHASED ITEMS FROM LASER THERAPY U BOOKSTORE\u003C/h3\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003ETo return a product purchased from our Laser Therapy U bookstore, call customer support \u003Ca href=\u0022mailto:cs@lasertherapyu.org\u0022\u003Ecs@lasertherapyu.org\u003C/a\u003E or call us at 1-678-825-4497, via fax 1-866-314-6706. Our support representative will give you a unique Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA) number and provide instructions on how to return the product. You may not return a product without an RMA number. The product will only be accepted as a return, if it is in as-new condition. Laser Therapy U will provide credit to either your credit card or via check. A re-stocking fee of 20% may apply.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EGEORGIA SALES TAX\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EFor orders made from within Georgia, a 8.0% sales tax will be applied. All other US based orders are tax free. International orders may require duties to be paid in your country for importation.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EGOVERNING LAW\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThis Agreement and the interpretation of its terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Georgia applicable to agreements negotiated, executed and performed wholly and solely within the State of Georgia. The parties agree that the State of Georgia\u0027s conflicts of laws rules shall not apply to this Agreement or any transaction performed by or under this Agreement. All sales are made Point of Atlanta, GA and sold FOB Atlanta, Georgia, USA\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003ENOTE\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThis site contains resources such as, but not limited to, Pubmed central (see copyright notice), Bookshelf (see bookshelf copyright notice), Omim, and Pubchem which incorporate material contributed or licensed by individuals, companies, or organizations that may be protected by U.S. and foreign copyright laws. All persons reproducing, redistributing, or making commercial use of this information are expected to adhere to the terms and conditions asserted by the copyright holder. Transmission or reproduction of protected items beyond that allowed by fair use (pdf) as defined in the copyright laws requires the written permission of the copyright owners.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003ELIABILITY\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EFor documents and software available from this server, the laser therapy u. Llc does not warrant or assume any legal liability or responsibility for the accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of any information, apparatus, product, or process disclosed.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EEXTERNAL LINKS\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003ESome lasertherapyu.org web pages may provide links to other internet sites for the convenience of users. Laser Therapy U. LLC is not responsible for the availability or content of these external sites, nor does Laser Therapy U. LLC endorse, warrant, or guarantee the products, services, or information described or offered at these other internet sites. Users cannot assume that the external sites will abide by the same privacy policy to which Laser Therapy U. LLC adheres. It is the responsibility of the user to examine the copyright and licensing restrictions of linked pages and to secure all necessary permissions.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EPOP-UP ADVERTISEMENTS\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EWhen visiting our web site, your web browser may produce pop-up advertisements. These advertisements were most likely produced by other web sites you visited or by third party software installed on your computer. The Laser Therapy U. LLC does not endorse or recommend products or services for which you may view a pop-up advertisement on your computer screen while visiting our site.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EMEDICAL INFORMATION\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EIt is not the intention of Laser Therapy U. LLC to provide specific medical advice but rather to provide users with information to better understand their health and their and patient\u0026rsquo;s diagnosed disorders. Specific medical advice will not be provided, and Laser Therapy U. LLC urges you to consult with a qualified physician for diagnosis and for answers to your personal questions.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003ECONDITIONS OF USE\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThis site is maintained by the Laser Therapy U. LLC and is protected by various provisions of title 18 of the U.S. code. Violations of title 18 are subject to criminal prosecution in a federal court. For site security purposes, as well as to ensure that this service remains available to all users, we use software programs to monitor traffic and to identify unauthorized attempts to upload or change information or otherwise cause damage. In the event of authorized law enforcement investigations and pursuant to any required legal process, information from these sources may be used to help identify an individual.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003ESECURITY\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003ELaser Therapy U. LLC maintains this site. For site security purposes and to ensure that this service remains available to all users, we use software programs to monitor traffic to identify unauthorized attempts to upload or change information, or otherwise cause damage. Causing damage to private computer systems is a violation of U.S. law and is subject to criminal prosecution in federal court. In the event of authorized law enforcement investigations, and pursuant to any required legal process, information from NLM Web logs may be used to help identify an individual.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ch2\u003ETHIRD-PARTY WEB SITES AND APPLICATIONS\u003C/h2\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThird-Party Web sites and Applications (TPWA) are Web-based technologies that are not exclusively operated or controlled by Laser Therapy U LLC. They may be hosted on a government, non-government, privately owned\u0026nbsp; web site or embedded on an LaserTherapyU.org Web page. TPWA technologies may make personally identifiable information (PII) available to Laser Therapy U.LLC, regardless of whether we request or collect it. In addition, other Web sites we link to or cooperate with may use a third-party to handle some aspect of an information collection (for example: contest nomination process). As a result, our stated privacy policy/notice may not apply.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EWe use these technologies to communicate and interact with you. Examples include social media Web sites such as Twitter and Facebook. Your activity on these non-government sites is governed by the security and privacy policies of those sites. When you use them, you are often sharing information with the general public, other users, and/or the group operating that site or application. We recommend you review the privacy policies of these sites before using them to ensure you understand how these third-party sites and applications might use your information. You may be able to adjust the privacy settings on your account.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThe list below includes the applications we use and their purposes. For any sites or applications that collect PII, this list also includes details on the information they collect and how Laser Therapy U. LLC protects your private information.\u003C/p\u003E\r\n\u003Cul\u003E\r\n    \u003Cli\u003EAuthorize.net/CyberSource Payment Processing Technology Services\u003C/li\u003E\r\n    \u003Cli\u003EUnited Parcel Services of America, Inc. Shipping Services\u003C/li\u003E\r\n    \u003Cli\u003EVzaar, Inc. Video Streaming Technology Services\u003C/li\u003E\r\n    \u003Cli\u003ECitrix Online, LLC Webinar Technology Services \u003C/li\u003E\r\n\u003C/ul\u003E\r\n\u003Cp\u003E \u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
